title: JRE review of 1254 with Dr. Phil
description:
Dr. Phil has been on the air for over 25 years and now is starting a podcast called “Phil in the blanks”. His conversation with Joe was really interesting and gives a good insight into how he thinks. Dr. Phil also covers the “catch me outside” girl and all the silliness there.
